Dialogue: 3,0:01:06.85,0:01:11.34,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有时，最微小的细节，也足以颠覆一切
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.85,0:01:11.34,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Sometimes, the smallest detail can change everything. 
Dialogue: 3,0:01:12.52,0:01:17.51,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,犯罪现场，或残酷，或丑陋，或恐怖
Dialogue: 2,0:01:12.52,0:01:17.51,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,A crime scene can be brutal, ugly, horrifying. 
Dialogue: 3,0:01:18.29,0:01:24.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,可一旦留下某种怪诞而费解之物，便会衍变为传奇
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.29,0:01:24.90,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But when something strange and unexplained is left behind, it crosses into legend.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:26.07,0:01:29.52,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这正是2013年杭州发生的故事，
Dialogue: 2,0:01:26.07,0:01:29.52,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And that's what happened in Hangzhou in 2013. 
Dialogue: 3,0:01:30.34,0:01:33.29,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一桩本该直截了当的谋杀案
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.34,0:01:33.29,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,A murder case that should have been straightforward 
Dialogue: 3,0:01:33.72,0:01:37.51,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,却因三件寻常之物，而在网络上声名狼藉
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.72,0:01:37.51,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,became infamous online because of three simple objects.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:38.97,0:01:41.34,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,几张扑克牌
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.97,0:01:41.34,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,A handful of playing cards. 
Dialogue: 3,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这几张牌，仿佛是来自逝者或凶手的讯息
Dialogue: 2,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.80,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Cards that seem like a message from the dead or the killer.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:50.67,0:01:54.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,2013年3月15日清晨
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.67,0:01:54.00,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,On the morning of March 15th, 2013, 
Dialogue: 3,0:01:54.50,0:01:58.88,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,杭州的一位年迈拾荒者，正沿世纪大道捡拾废品
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.50,0:01:58.88,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,an elderly scavenger in Hangzhou was collecting scraps along the Century Avenue.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:00.85,0:02:05.27,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在良熟村附近，他发现了一个被遗弃的大纸箱
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.85,0:02:05.27,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,He spotted a large cardboard box abandoned near Liangshu Village. 
Dialogue: 3,0:02:06.05,0:02:08.54,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,起初并无异常
Dialogue: 2,0:02:06.05,0:02:08.54,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,At first, it was nothing unusual 
Dialogue: 3,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,直到他瞥见箱底渗出的血迹
Dialogue: 2,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.55,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,until he noticed blood seeping through the bottom.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:13.08,0:02:16.25,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,惊恐之下，他唤来一名环卫工
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.08,0:02:16.25,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Frightened, he called over a street cleaner. 
Dialogue: 3,0:02:16.25,0:02:18.54,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,二人合力撬开纸箱
Dialogue: 2,0:02:16.25,0:02:18.54,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Together, they pried it open. 
Dialogue: 3,0:02:19.02,0:02:21.59,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,里面竟是一具尸体
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.02,0:02:21.59,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Inside was a human body. 
Dialogue: 3,0:02:22.26,0:02:24.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,警方迅速抵达现场
Dialogue: 2,0:02:22.26,0:02:24.37,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The police arrived quickly.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:24.77,0:02:28.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,尸身属于一位年轻女子，伤痕累累
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.77,0:02:28.26,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And the body belonged to a young woman. Badly scarred. 
Dialogue: 3,0:02:29.02,0:02:33.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,确认已死亡数日，时间大约在3月10日前后
Dialogue: 2,0:02:29.02,0:02:33.37,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And was confirmed dead for several days. Sometime around March 10th.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这显然是一起凶杀案
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.00,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And it was very clearly a homicide. 
Dialogue: 3,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.43,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她曾遭殴打、捆绑，并被塞入箱中
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.43,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,She had been beaten, bound, and stuffed into the box.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:41.02,0:02:43.58,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但勘察人员还发现了别的东西
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.02,0:02:43.58,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But investigators found something else. 
Dialogue: 3,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.85,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,三张扑克牌与尸身共存箱内
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.85,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Three playing cards inside with their body. 
Dialogue: 3,0:02:47.48,0:02:52.66,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,黑桃五、方块J和黑桃K
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.48,0:02:52.66,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The Five of Spades. The Jack of Diamonds. And the King of Spades.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:53.39,0:02:56.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这几张牌与现场的残暴景象格格不入
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.39,0:02:56.80,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And the cards didn't match the brutality of the scene. 
Dialogue: 3,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它们看起来像是被刻意放置于此
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.45,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,They looked like they were placed there on purpose.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:00.19,0:03:03.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,警方核查了本地的失踪人口记录，一无所获
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.19,0:03:03.60,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Police checked local missing persons. And nothing matched. 
Dialogue: 3,0:03:04.15,0:03:09.27,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,于是他们将受害者的衣物、纹身以及那三张牌的照片公之于网
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.15,0:03:09.27,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,So they released photos of the victim's clothing, her tattoos, and the three cards online.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:10.22,0:03:13.61,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,案件就此在中国各大论坛上引爆
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.22,0:03:13.61,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And that's when the case exploded across Chinese forums. 
Dialogue: 3,0:03:13.61,0:03:16.10,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,网民们剖析着每一条线索
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.61,0:03:16.10,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Netizens dissected every clue.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.32,0:03:20.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有人说，KJ5意为“快救我”
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.32,0:03:20.20,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Some said, KJ5 meant help me. 
Dialogue: 3,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.01,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有人则认为它是一个车牌号
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.01,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Others thought it was a license plate code. 
Dialogue: 3,0:03:23.64,0:03:27.01,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,甚至有人推测，这几个字母对应着凶手的姓名缩写
Dialogue: 2,0:03:23.64,0:03:27.01,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And some even speculated the letters matched the killer's initials.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:27.92,0:03:33.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这几张牌，将一桩谋杀案变成了一桩充满密码、象征、近乎电影情节的悬案
Dialogue: 2,0:03:27.92,0:03:33.26,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The cards turned to murder into a mystery that felt coded, symbolic, and almost cinematic.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但对警方而言，问题更为纯粹
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.75,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But for the detectives, the problem was simpler. 
Dialogue: 3,0:03:38.10,0:03:40.43,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们甚至连她是谁都不知道
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.10,0:03:40.43,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,They didn't know who she even was.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:41.85,0:03:44.85,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然而网民们却不肯罢休
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.85,0:03:44.85,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But people online refused to let it go. 
Dialogue: 3,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.89,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,人们追查到售卖她衣物的店铺
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.89,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,People tracked down the shops that sold her clothing.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:47.89,0:03:51.28,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,纹身爱好者在档案中搜寻相同的设计
Dialogue: 2,0:03:47.89,0:03:51.28,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Tattoo enthusiasts searched archives for the same design. 
Dialogue: 3,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.87,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还有人将她的照片与失踪人员通告逐一比对
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.87,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And others compared her photo to the missing person notices.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.98,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,尽管大部分努力都徒劳无功
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.98,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And while most of it led to nowhere, 
Dialogue: 3,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,却让此案持续停留在公众的视野里
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.80,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,it kept the case alive in the public eye.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:02.53,0:04:05.61,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,终于，一条线索改变了一切
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.53,0:04:05.61,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And finally, one tip changed everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:06.95,0:04:09.76,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,近一个月后的4月10日
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.95,0:04:09.76,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,On April 10th, nearly a month later, 
Dialogue: 3,0:04:09.76,0:04:13.73,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一位杭州市民报告称，他曾见过这名女子
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.76,0:04:13.73,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,a Hangzhou resident reported that they had seen a woman before,
Dialogue: 3,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.88,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她住在余杭的联盟社区
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.88,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,living in the Lianmeng community, in Yuhang.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,警方随即走访了那个社区
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.37,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Police canvassed the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:20.02,0:04:23.22,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一家超市老板忆起一件怪事
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.02,0:04:23.22,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,A supermarket owner remembered something odd.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:23.81,0:04:28.29,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一个身材微胖、身高约170厘米的男子
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.81,0:04:28.29,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,A slightly overweight man, about 170 centimeters tall, 
Dialogue: 3,0:04:28.29,0:04:31.14,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,买了两卷厚实的透明胶带
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.29,0:04:31.14,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,buying two rolls of thick, transparent tape.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:31.93,0:04:34.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,与捆绑尸身所用的胶带是同一类型
Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.93,0:04:34.77,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The same kind of tape used to bind a body.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.39,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,监控录像确认了他的身份
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.39,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And security cameras confirmed his identity.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他姓何
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.26,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,His name was He.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.81,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,邻居们说，受害者是他的女友
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.81,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And neighbors said the victim was his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:44.52,0:04:48.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,当警方在一家服装厂找到他时，他供认不讳
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.52,0:04:48.50,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,When police tracked him down at the garment factory, he confessed.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他和后来被确认为“程某”的受害者
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.60,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,He and the victim later identified as Cheng
Dialogue: 3,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.14,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,自2012年12月开始交往
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.14,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,had been dating since December of 2012.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:56.45,0:04:58.09,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但他嫉妒心极强
Dialogue: 2,0:04:56.45,0:04:58.09,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But he was very jealous.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.63,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他看到她在网上与另一名男子聊天
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.63,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,He saw her chatting with another man online.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.87,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,便要求她停止
Dialogue: 2,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.87,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,He demanded her to stop.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:02.87,0:05:05.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而当她拒绝时，他的怒火被点燃了
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.87,0:05:05.92,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And when she refused, his anger boiled over.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:06.76,0:05:08.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,3月10日，他彻底失控
Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.76,0:05:08.70,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And on March 10th, he snapped.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.47,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他勒死了她，用胶带捆绑其尸身
Dialogue: 2,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.47,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,He strangled her, taped her body, 
Dialogue: 3,0:05:11.47,0:05:15.56,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,将其塞入箱中，然后弃于路边
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.47,0:05:15.56,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,stuffed her into a box, and dumped it on the roadside.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.29,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,当警方追问那些扑克牌时
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.29,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And when the detectives pressed him on the cards, 
Dialogue: 3,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.86,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他说他毫不知情
Dialogue: 2,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.86,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,he said he had no idea.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:22.52,0:05:26.61,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他说在挣扎中，想必是撞倒了一个抽屉
Dialogue: 2,0:05:22.52,0:05:26.61,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,He says that in the struggle, he must have knocked over a drawer.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:26.61,0:05:30.01,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,那些牌应该是掉了出来，混进了箱子里
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.61,0:05:30.01,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And the cards must have fallen out and gotten mixed into the box.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这是一个平淡无奇的解释
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.32,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It's a very mundane explanation.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:33.85,0:05:38.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但在他坦白之时，互联网已将这几张牌塑造成神话
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.85,0:05:38.45,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But by the time he confessed, the internet had already transformed the cards into myth.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,将一桩简单的凶杀案
Dialogue: 2,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.95,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Turning a simple domestic killing 
Dialogue: 3,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.52,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,演变为中国现代“奇案”之一
Dialogue: 2,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.52,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,into one of the eeriest modern cases in China.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.07,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而最终的真相是丑陋的
Dialogue: 2,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.07,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And in the end, the truth was ugly.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.62,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一桩因嫉妒引发的罪行
Dialogue: 2,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.62,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,A crime of jealousy.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一个女人的生命被夺走
Dialogue: 2,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,A woman's life taken.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.18,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她所信任之人亲自动手
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.18,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,By someone she trusted.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.15,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而离奇的是
Dialogue: 2,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.15,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And what's weird is, 
Dialogue: 3,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.49,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,人们所铭记的，不仅仅是罪行本身 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.49,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,what people remember isn't just the crime.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.86,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而是那些牌
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.86,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It's the cards.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:58.53,0:06:01.41,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,因为仅仅三张毫无意义的纸片
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.53,0:06:01.41,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Because just three meaningless scraps of paper
Dialogue: 3,0:06:01.41,0:06:05.05,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,却创造了一个比案件本身更长久的故事
Dialogue: 2,0:06:01.41,0:06:05.05,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,created a story that lived far longer than the case itself.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}﻿梦境本应是无害的
Dialogue: 3,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.07,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}潜意识转瞬即逝的碎片
Dialogue: 3,0:06:38.27,0:06:42.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但如果我说，梦能引导警方找到藏尸地点呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:06:44.12,0:06:47.44,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}2008年，在吉林省的一个小镇上
Dialogue: 3,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样的事情真实发生了
Dialogue: 3,0:06:51.17,0:06:54.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一名男子失踪了，随后人们发现了他带血的衣物
Dialogue: 3,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}随后他的姐姐做了一个梦
Dialogue: 3,0:06:58.35,0:07:01.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一个准确告诉她去哪里寻找尸体的梦
Dialogue: 3,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}故事还要从张永成此人说起
Dialogue: 3,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.65,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是一位居住在长白山市的商贩
Dialogue: 3,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他为人友好，广受欢迎
Dialogue: 3,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}靠买卖山货为生
Dialogue: 3,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}2008年6月11日
Dialogue: 3,0:07:23.97,0:07:28.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在帮助他的邻居兼生意伙伴刘晓林整理完货物之后
Dialogue: 3,0:07:29.47,0:07:33.47,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他在晚十点左右穿着迷彩夹克离开了刘晓林家
Dialogue: 3,0:07:35.75,0:07:38.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从刘家到他家走路只要一分钟
Dialogue: 3,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但这条路他却再也没能走完
Dialogue: 3,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}日子一天天过去，没有人再见过他
Dialogue: 3,0:07:46.15,0:07:49.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一周后，村里人发现了奇怪的东西：
Dialogue: 3,0:07:49.70,0:07:53.25,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}被压在柴火堆下的一件迷彩衣
Dialogue: 3,0:07:53.75,0:07:55.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}浸满了鲜血
Dialogue: 3,0:07:57.17,0:08:00.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}警方确认这件衬衫属于张永成
Dialogue: 3,0:08:01.35,0:08:04.40,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}奇怪的是，胸口处有一个圆形的洞
Dialogue: 3,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是刀割，而是更血腥的痕迹
Dialogue: 3,0:08:09.62,0:08:12.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}布料周围散落着几缕头发
Dialogue: 3,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}调查人员立刻意识到这不是一场意外
Dialogue: 3,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.62,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而是一起谋杀
Dialogue: 3,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}警方搜查整个村庄时
Dialogue: 3,0:08:22.80,0:08:26.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们注意到了刘晓林家和张家之间的沙堆
Dialogue: 3,0:08:27.95,0:08:30.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}成群的苍蝇在上面嗡嗡飞行
Dialogue: 3,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.65,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}警员向下挖掘后
Dialogue: 3,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又发现了深色的污渍—血液
Dialogue: 3,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}正渗入泥土中
Dialogue: 3,0:08:39.15,0:08:42.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}邻居们还报告说，在张永成失踪的6月11日晚
Dialogue: 3,0:08:42.72,0:08:45.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}曾听到沙堆附近传来巨响
Dialogue: 3,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.63,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很明显，这里发生过暴力事件
Dialogue: 3,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但警方却始终找不到张永成的尸体
Dialogue: 3,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}正当调查人员束手无策时
Dialogue: 3,0:08:58.40,0:09:02.67,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}张永成的姐姐张燕找到了警方
Dialogue: 3,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.85,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她说她做了一个梦
Dialogue: 3,0:09:05.22,0:09:07.42,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她弟弟在梦里跟她说了话
Dialogue: 3,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}准确地描述了自己被埋葬的位置
Dialogue: 3,0:09:10.70,0:09:14.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}往西，沿着铁路线，在铁轨的南边
Dialogue: 3,0:09:16.17,0:09:18.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}警方当然不会相信这种超自然线索
Dialogue: 3,0:09:19.02,0:09:20.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但为了安慰这位悲伤的亲属
Dialogue: 3,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们还是派出了一个小组前去调查
Dialogue: 3,0:09:24.05,0:09:26.42,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而他们的发现震惊了所有人
Dialogue: 3,0:09:28.02,0:09:30.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在铁路线旁一块被动过的土地上
Dialogue: 3,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}离地表约两米深处
Dialogue: 3,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.27,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}正是张永成的尸体
Dialogue: 3,0:09:36.57,0:09:40.85,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他身上有十三处刀伤，其中一刀刺穿了心脏
Dialogue: 3,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.40,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他正是在失踪的那天晚上被杀害的
Dialogue: 3,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.85,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梦的指示让案件调查产生了新的方向
Dialogue: 3,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.99,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}警方甚至怀疑张燕本人是否涉案
Dialogue: 3,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.67,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}毕竟
Dialogue: 3,0:09:53.70,0:09:56.52,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她怎么可能如此准确地知道埋尸地点呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:09:57.57,0:10:01.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但她只有1米56高，体型瘦弱
Dialogue: 3,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.27,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}根本不可能挖出这么大一个墓穴
Dialogue: 3,0:10:04.05,0:10:07.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}更别说如何搬动张永成两百多斤的尸体了
Dialogue: 3,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.15,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}于是警方的注意力又回到了他身边的村民身上
Dialogue: 3,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.27,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事情真相很快便浮出水面
Dialogue: 3,0:10:15.00,0:10:19.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}张永成和他的生意伙伴刘晓林有过一段恋情
Dialogue: 3,0:10:20.85,0:10:24.47,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但刘晓林已是有夫之妇，她的丈夫是铁路工人顾大海
Dialogue: 3,0:10:25.87,0:10:28.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且在张永成之前，刘晓林还有另一个情夫
Dialogue: 3,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}名叫韩志刚
Dialogue: 3,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不仅仅是一起谋杀案
Dialogue: 3,0:10:34.47,0:10:37.35,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}更是一张由痴迷和不忠交织而成的复杂关系网
Dialogue: 3,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}起初，刘晓林的丈夫顾大海被警方列为嫌疑人
Dialogue: 3,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.03,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}作为一名铁路工人，他对埋尸一带非常熟悉
Dialogue: 3,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.21,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此极有可能将尸体埋在铁路沿线的是他
Dialogue: 3,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但证据并不吻合
Dialogue: 3,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}顾大海坚称自己没有作案动机
Dialogue: 3,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}甚至还说张永成是他的好铁子
Dialogue: 3,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.42,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}随后另一个人物出现了——
Dialogue: 3,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}刘晓林的前情人韩志刚
Dialogue: 3,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他占有欲强、嫉妒心重
Dialogue: 3,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.35,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对刘晓林移情别恋一事心怀怨恨
Dialogue: 3,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而就在张永成尸体被发现之后
Dialogue: 3,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.15,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}韩志刚就“恰好”消失了
Dialogue: 3,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}警方随即加紧了调查
Dialogue: 3,0:11:16.82,0:11:20.12,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}调查发现，韩志刚在谋杀当晚
Dialogue: 3,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}借了村民的一辆独轮车
Dialogue: 3,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}声称需要搬运沙子
Dialogue: 3,0:11:25.25,0:11:28.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而当独轮车被送回时，已经被擦洗得一尘不染
Dialogue: 3,0:11:30.17,0:11:34.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}经过进一步检测，警方发现了微量的血迹
Dialogue: 3,0:11:35.15,0:11:36.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也就是张永成的血
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.90,0:11:39.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}随后是最后一块拼图
Dialogue: 3,0:11:40.07,0:11:43.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在韩志刚家院子里的一个浴缸下面，藏着一个塑料袋
Dialogue: 3,0:11:44.57,0:11:48.07,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}警方在袋中找到了两把仍沾有张永成血迹的刀
Dialogue: 3,0:11:48.60,0:11:52.12,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}走投无路之下，韩志刚坦白了罪行
Dialogue: 3,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}2008年6月11日
Dialogue: 3,0:12:00.27,0:12:03.27,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}韩志刚撞见张永成离开了卢小林的家
Dialogue: 3,0:12:03.92,0:12:06.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一怒之下，他用刀袭击了张永成
Dialogue: 3,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}随后发生了一场激烈的搏斗
Dialogue: 3,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}张永成奋力反抗，衣服也随即撕破
Dialogue: 3,0:12:13.17,0:12:16.02,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但最终，他不敌韩志刚而身中13刀
Dialogue: 3,0:12:16.37,0:12:18.67,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}倒在了沙堆边
Dialogue: 3,0:12:19.00,0:12:22.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}韩志刚随后用独轮车将尸体运到铁路沿线
Dialogue: 3,0:12:22.90,0:12:25.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后将他深埋入土中
Dialogue: 3,0:12:26.10,0:12:29.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是纯粹出于嫉妒心而犯案，仅此而已
Dialogue: 3,0:12:31.40,0:12:33.52,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但这起案件之所以臭名昭著
Dialogue: 3,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.25,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是因为其中最令人发毛的细节
Dialogue: 3,0:12:36.50,0:12:37.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}——揭示藏尸处的梦
Dialogue: 3,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}张永成的姐姐
Dialogue: 3,0:12:39.85,0:12:44.05,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论是出于巧合、直觉，还是某种无法解释的力量
Dialogue: 3,0:12:44.12,0:12:46.07,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她直接指出了藏尸之处
Dialogue: 3,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.47,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她的弟弟也终于得以安息
Dialogue: 3,0:12:51.60,0:12:55.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大多数谋杀案要么靠证据侦破，要么靠供词
Dialogue: 3,0:12:55.55,0:12:59.12,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但这起案件却是由一个梦侦破的
Dialogue: 3,0:13:26.75,0:13:30.06,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,2014年 在那个神奇的山东招远市
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.75,0:13:30.06,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,In 2014, in Zhao Yun City, China, 
Dialogue: 3,0:13:30.36,0:13:35.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一家麦当劳成为了被监控拍下的top5哈人犯罪现场之一
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.36,0:13:35.17,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,the McDonald's became the scene of one of the most disturbing crimes caught on surveillance.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:36.20,0:13:40.39,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这是一场发生在家庭、孩子和顾客面前的血腥谋杀
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.20,0:13:40.39,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,A murder carried out in front of families, children, and customers.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:41.56,0:13:45.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而凶手们 则相信自己正在对抗“恶灵”
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.56,0:13:45.37,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,All by a group who believed they were fighting evil spirits.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,那是5月28日 一个五指不见伸手的夜晚
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.00,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It was the evening of May 28th.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:51.46,0:13:57.05,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,37岁的吴硕艳是在一位在附近一家服装店工作的销售员
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.46,0:13:57.05,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Wu Zhao Yun, 37 years old, a salesperson who worked at a nearby clothing store.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:58.06,0:14:02.03,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,已经下班的她在麦当劳等着家人们的到来
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.06,0:14:02.03,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,After work, she was waiting at a McDonald's for her family to arrive.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:04.43,0:14:10.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,大约晚上9点 六个人走了进来 包括五名成年人和一个少年
Dialogue: 2,0:14:04.43,0:14:10.60,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Around 9 pm, a group of six people entered, a mix of adults, and even one teenager.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:11.35,0:14:13.44,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但他们不是来点餐的
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.35,0:14:13.44,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But they weren't there to order food.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:14.07,0:14:19.96,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们是来传教的
Dialogue: 2,0:14:14.07,0:14:19.96,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Instead, they started preaching to customers, telling them about their religious beliefs.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.43,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但这还没完
Dialogue: 2,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.43,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But it didn't just stop there.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:23.75,0:14:29.83,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们还要所有人的手机号码 声称他们将来还会联系
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.75,0:14:29.83,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It began demanding everyone's cell phone numbers, claiming they needed them to future contact.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:34.52,0:14:40.36,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而当吴数次拒绝他们时 他们就开始向她发起攻击
Dialogue: 2,0:14:34.52,0:14:40.36,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And when Wu refused, not once, but twice, they turned on her.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:40.68,0:14:43.11,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这群人喊道 她是个恶魔
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.68,0:14:43.11,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The group shouted that she was an evil spirit.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:43.72,0:14:47.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然后他们就开始在餐厅里所有人的面前攻击她
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.72,0:14:47.72,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And then, in front of the entire restaurant, they began attacking her.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:48.04,0:14:50.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们使用的武器包括椅子、拖把和他们的脚
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.04,0:14:50.20,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Chairs, mops, and their feet.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.66,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这些动作毫不留情
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.66,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The beating was merciless.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:54.84,0:14:58.65,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而任何试图干预的人则都受到了同样的威胁
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.84,0:14:58.65,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And anyone who tried to intervene was threatened with the same fate.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:00.15,0:15:03.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而监控拍下了这一切
Dialogue: 2,0:15:00.15,0:15:03.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and the CCTV cameras recorded everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:05.07,0:15:10.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,顾客们惊恐地不断后退 而吴则在众目睽睽之下被殴打致死
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.07,0:15:10.37,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Customers backed away in fear as Wu was beaten to death and in full public view.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:14.18,0:15:18.22,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,当警察到达时 他们逮捕了六名袭击者
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.18,0:15:18.22,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,When police finally arrived, they arrested all six attackers.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:20.56,0:15:27.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,中国政府的通报称 凶手是“全能神”教会的成员
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.56,0:15:27.94,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The Chinese government quickly reported that the killers were members of the Eastern Lightning cult.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.58,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这是一个备受争议的、根据基督教瞎编的教派
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.58,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It's a controversial Christian-inspired sect.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:30.58,0:15:36.58,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,该教派成立于1990年代 长期以来被国家列入邪教的清单
Dialogue: 2,0:15:30.58,0:15:36.58,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Found in the 1990s, which has been long accused by the state of being a dangerous cult.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:37.61,0:15:44.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,全能神教会 是一个受基督教启发的团体 于1990年代在中国成立
Dialogue: 2,0:15:37.61,0:15:44.97,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Eastern Lightning, or the Church of Almighty God, is a Christian-inspired group founded in China in the 1990s.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.48,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,据该团体的教典称 基督已经回归
Dialogue: 2,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.48,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,According to the group, Christ is returned, 
Dialogue: 3,0:15:48.48,0:15:52.85,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但祂以一位中国女性的形式出现 而他们的追随者必须接受他们的教义
Dialogue: 2,0:15:48.48,0:15:52.85,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,but in the form of a Chinese woman, and their followers must embrace your teachings.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:53.45,0:15:56.49,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,政府将其列为邪教
Dialogue: 2,0:15:53.45,0:15:56.49,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And the government labels this as an evil cult.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:58.25,0:16:01.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,关键是 这个教派早就不是第一次出来跳了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:58.25,0:16:01.95,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And the thing is, this cult isn't even new to controversy.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:02.56,0:16:11.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,多年来 当局指控“全能神”犯有强制改宗、财务剥削、家庭暴力和骚扰等罪行
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.56,0:16:06.79,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Over the years, authorities have accused Eastern Lightning of forced conversations, 
Dialogue: 2,0:16:06.79,0:16:11.77,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,financial exploitation, domestic abuse, and harassment.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.69,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,据报道 在一些农村地区
Dialogue: 2,0:16:12.17,0:16:17.97,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,In some rural areas, reports say they apply high-pressure tactics on families to join or donate.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:13.69,0:16:17.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们对家庭施加高压策略 要求他们加入或捐款
Dialogue: 3,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.69,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,对于这次麦当劳杀人事件
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.69,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,In the context of the McDonald's killing, 
Dialogue: 3,0:16:21.69,0:16:28.51,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,官方声称那六名袭击者来自“全能神”内部的一个奇怪的分支
Dialogue: 2,0:16:21.69,0:16:28.51,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,the official narrative claims that the six attackers came from a dissident or strange subgroup within Eastern Lightning.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:29.37,0:16:32.33,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们可能不受教会中央的管理
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.37,0:16:32.33,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Maybe not fully under the church's central control.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:32.82,0:16:38.73,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但他们的行为符合一些更激进的邪教信仰 比如将非信徒视为恶灵
Dialogue: 2,0:16:32.82,0:16:38.73,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,But their actions align with some of the more radical cult beliefs, rejecting non-believers as evil spirits, 
Dialogue: 3,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.93,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,要求服从 如要求提供电话号码或联系方式
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.93,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,, demanding submission, as in phone numbers or contact, 
Dialogue: 3,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.09,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还有暴力地强制执行他们的教义
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.09,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and enforcing their doctrine violently.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,袭击者接受了审判
Dialogue: 2,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.82,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And the attackers were put on trial.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:54.06,0:16:59.41,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,录像、证人和供词等都是判死他们的铁证
Dialogue: 2,0:16:54.06,0:16:59.41,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The footage, the witnesses, and the confessions all made it impossible to deny what happened.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:00.94,0:17:05.86,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,团体中的两人 包括主犯 被判处死刑 并于2015年执行
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.94,0:17:03.16,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Two of the group, including the ringleaders, 
Dialogue: 2,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.86,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,Senten to death and executed in 2015.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:07.16,0:17:09.33,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,其他人则被判处长期监禁
Dialogue: 2,0:17:07.16,0:17:09.33,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The others received long prison sentences.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:10.25,0:17:15.18,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,尘埃落定之后 这个案件成为了现代中国最臭名昭著的邪教犯罪
Dialogue: 2,0:17:10.25,0:17:15.18,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And in the aftermath, the case became one of the most infamous cult crimes in modern China.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:16.25,0:17:21.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它还导致了突袭、大规模逮捕和铁拳
Dialogue: 2,0:17:16.25,0:17:21.32,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It sparked raids, mass arrests, and a crackdown on the Church of Almighty God.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:23.15,0:17:26.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,招远麦当劳命案至今仍是一个沉痛的警示
Dialogue: 2,0:17:23.15,0:17:26.72,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,The Xiaoyan McDonald's murder remains a disturbing reminder
Dialogue: 3,0:17:26.92,0:17:30.11,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它向我们展示了信仰是如何走向狂热
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.92,0:17:30.11,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,of how belief, worked into fanaticism, 
Dialogue: 3,0:17:30.56,0:17:33.40,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,并最终在最寻常不过的地方演变为骇人的暴力的
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.56,0:17:33.40,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,and erupted into violence, in the most ordinary places.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.56,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在这个案件中 监控捕捉到的不仅仅是图像
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.56,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It's a case where surveillance didn't just capture an image.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:37.80,0:17:43.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它捕捉到的是一个意识形态 是一个模糊了信仰和妄想界限的信仰体系
Dialogue: 2,0:17:37.80,0:17:43.60,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,It captured an entire ideology, a belief system that blurred the line between faith and delusion.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:45.66,0:17:53.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它还向世界展示了当一个团体认为自己的谋杀实为救赎时的恐怖
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.66,0:17:53.95,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,And it showed the world of how truly terrifying it is when a group convinces themselves that killing isn't murder, as salvation.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:20.81,0:18:24.50,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,On the Chinese internet, scandals come and go.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.81,0:18:24.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在中国的网络世界里，丑闻此起彼伏
Dialogue: 3,0:18:24.50,0:18:29.91,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But few have ever reached the scale, or the strangeness, of Sister Hong.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:24.50,0:18:29.91,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但鲜有事件能和红姐一样出名与诡异
Dialogue: 3,0:18:29.91,0:18:34.13,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,A figure who looked like a woman, who spoke like one.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.91,0:18:34.13,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他打扮成女人，言行举止也在模仿女人
Dialogue: 3,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.92,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Who lured in hundreds of men.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,诱骗了n名男性
Dialogue: 3,0:18:36.92,0:18:41.06,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But behind the wig, and the mask, wasn't a sister at all.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.92,0:18:41.06,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在假发和伪装背后，他根本不是什么“姐”
Dialogue: 3,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.87,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,It was a man.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.87,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,就是一男的
Dialogue: 3,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.65,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,A man who spent years recording, deceiving, 
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.65,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一个花费数年时间，通过偷拍、欺骗
Dialogue: 3,0:18:45.65,0:18:49.67,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,and profiting off a secret empire of private videos.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:45.65,0:18:49.67,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,贩卖私密视频建立起地下帝国的男人
Dialogue: 3,0:18:49.67,0:18:55.29,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And the story is how one disguised figure, full thousands, destroyed lives.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:49.67,0:18:55.29,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这是一个男人欺骗无数男人，让他们身败名裂的故事
Dialogue: 3,0:18:55.29,0:18:58.30,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And left behind a digital scar so disturbing, 
Dialogue: 2,0:18:55.29,0:18:58.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,红姐在中国互联网留下了不可磨灭的印记
Dialogue: 3,0:18:58.30,0:19:01.01,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,the Chinese press called it the viral event of the year.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.30,0:19:01.01,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,被中国媒体评为「年度最轰动网络事件」
Dialogue: 3,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.99,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The story begins with an online profile.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.99,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,事件起源于一个账号的简介页
Dialogue: 3,0:19:08.99,0:19:11.11,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,A woman, caked in white makeup.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:08.99,0:19:11.11,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一个满脸厚厚白粉的“女人”
Dialogue: 3,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.86,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Thick red lipstick.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.86,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,死亡大红唇
Dialogue: 3,0:19:12.86,0:19:16.29,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Sometimes even hiding behind a surgical mask.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.86,0:19:16.29,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有时候戴个蓝口罩把脸遮住
Dialogue: 3,0:19:16.29,0:19:19.05,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,She called herself, Sister Hong.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:16.29,0:19:19.05,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,以「红姐」自称
Dialogue: 3,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.87,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And at first glance, nothing about her profile screamed danger.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.87,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,乍一看，她的账号挺无害的
Dialogue: 3,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.91,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,She was just another face on dating apps and chat groups.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.91,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这在约会软件和群聊里很常见
Dialogue: 3,0:19:27.41,0:19:30.13,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But Hong's appeal didn't lie in beauty.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.41,0:19:30.13,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但红姐的吸引力并不在于外貌
Dialogue: 3,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.73,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,It laid in curiosity.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.73,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而是一种神秘感
Dialogue: 3,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.41,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Her look was unsettling.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.41,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她长得十分惊悚
Dialogue: 3,0:19:35.41,0:19:36.95,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Almost uncanny.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.41,0:19:36.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,甚至有几分诡异
Dialogue: 3,0:19:36.95,0:19:40.12,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And yet, men still messaged her.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.95,0:19:40.12,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,就这样，还是会有男的私信她
Dialogue: 3,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.99,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Many even agreed to meet.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.99,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}主动约她见面
Dialogue: 3,0:19:43.33,0:19:45.73,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,When they arrived, they found rules.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.33,0:19:45.73,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,见面以后，会发现有点不对劲
Dialogue: 3,0:19:45.73,0:19:47.90,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Strange ones.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:45.73,0:19:47.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,红姐的要求不走寻常路
Dialogue: 3,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.68,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,She didn't accept cash for her services.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.68,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,她不收现金
Dialogue: 3,0:19:50.68,0:19:53.21,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Instead, men were told to bring items.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.68,0:19:53.21,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,带东西来即可
Dialogue: 3,0:19:53.21,0:19:56.11,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,A watermelon. A basket of vegetables.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:53.21,0:19:56.11,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,比如西瓜、果篮
Dialogue: 3,0:19:56.11,0:19:58.39,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Sometimes even half-used cooking oil.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.11,0:19:58.39,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,甚至用过的油都来了
Dialogue: 3,0:20:00.93,0:20:02.13,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And it wasn't random.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.93,0:20:02.13,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这并非随意的要求
Dialogue: 3,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.93,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,It was actually a cover.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.93,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,实则是刻意设下的掩护
Dialogue: 3,0:20:04.75,0:20:08.81,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,By avoiding financial transactions, Sister Hong left no paper trail.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:04.75,0:20:08.81,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,不用金钱交易，就不存在经济往来
Dialogue: 3,0:20:08.81,0:20:10.30,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,No receipts.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:08.81,0:20:10.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,没有收据
Dialogue: 3,0:20:10.30,0:20:12.26,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,No bank transfers.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:10.30,0:20:12.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,没有转账记录
Dialogue: 3,0:20:12.26,0:20:14.74,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And nothing to tie her encounters to the law.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:12.26,0:20:14.74,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,也就无法用法律界定她的行为
Dialogue: 3,0:20:17.11,0:20:21.06,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But the strangest rule of all was the lights.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:17.11,0:20:21.06,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,最诡异的一条规矩是
Dialogue: 3,0:20:21.06,0:20:23.10,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The men weren't allowed to switch them off.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:21.06,0:20:23.10,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,红姐不让这些男的关灯
Dialogue: 3,0:20:24.17,0:20:28.91,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And whenever someone tried, Sister Hong would calmly get up and flick them back on.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:24.17,0:20:28.91,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,就算你把灯关上，红姐也会若无其事的把灯打开
Dialogue: 3,0:20:30.53,0:20:33.64,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And they didn't know why, but she did.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:30.53,0:20:33.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这些男的还被蒙在鼓里，而红姐心里一清二楚
Dialogue: 3,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.12,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because every moment was actively being recorded.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.12,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为红姐在实时录制他们的行为
Dialogue: 3,0:20:41.68,0:20:46.18,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Behind those bright lights, hidden cameras were installed around the apartment.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.68,0:20:46.18,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在明亮的灯光下，公寓的各个角落都藏着摄像头
Dialogue: 3,0:20:46.18,0:20:49.26,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Men came and went, unaware of their faces, their bodies, 
Dialogue: 2,0:20:46.18,0:20:49.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,男人们来来去去，殊不知脸和金箔被拍的一清二楚
Dialogue: 3,0:20:49.26,0:20:51.80,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,and their secrets were being preserved on hard drives.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:49.26,0:20:51.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然后存进红姐的硬盘里
Dialogue: 3,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.62,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And for years, nothing leaked.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.62,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,很多年来，这些视频都没有流出
Dialogue: 3,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.91,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Sister Hong operated quietly.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.91,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,红姐一直在暗中活动
Dialogue: 3,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.39,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Clips were distributed in close groups.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.39,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这些视频只发给小圈子的观众
Dialogue: 3,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.46,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Sometimes on Telegram.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有部分发在电报
Dialogue: 3,0:21:02.46,0:21:05.41,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Sometimes sold directly to paying subscribers.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:02.46,0:21:05.41,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,或是发给订阅付费用户
Dialogue: 3,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.97,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,$20 a month for access.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,一月20刀
Dialogue: 3,0:21:08.97,0:21:11.38,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Private chats buzzing with new uploads.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:08.97,0:21:11.38,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,私联小群中不断有人议论最新视频
Dialogue: 3,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.36,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The demand was huge.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.36,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而且有很多人要
Dialogue: 3,0:21:13.39,0:21:15.33,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And so were the numbers.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:13.39,0:21:15.33,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,视频也就越拍越多
Dialogue: 3,0:21:15.33,0:21:22.00,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,By mid-2025, Hong had allegedly recorded encounters with well over a thousand men.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:15.33,0:21:22.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,到2025年年中，据称红姐已录下与一千多名男子的“互动”
Dialogue: 3,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.26,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Some came back repeatedly.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,其中一些还是回头客
Dialogue: 3,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.56,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And one man was nicknamed Four Seasons Brother.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.56,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,就比如说「四季哥」
Dialogue: 3,0:21:27.56,0:21:30.55,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Because he returned once per season.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:27.56,0:21:30.55,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他一个季度来一次
Dialogue: 3,0:21:30.55,0:21:33.54,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The entire operation was a hidden world.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:30.55,0:21:33.54,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,本来红姐的视频只在小范围内传播
Dialogue: 3,0:21:33.54,0:21:36.90,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Until one subscriber broke the silence.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:33.54,0:21:36.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}直到一个付费用户泄了密
Dialogue: 3,0:21:38.68,0:21:42.41,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And one day, almost the entire archive was leaked.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:38.68,0:21:42.41,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在某一天把几乎所有视频都泄了出去
Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.74,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Hundreds of hours of uncensored footage.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.74,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,几百小时的无码录像
Dialogue: 3,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.93,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Faces clearly visible.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.93,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,人脸清晰可辨
Dialogue: 3,0:21:46.93,0:21:50.80,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And within days, it spread across Chinese social media like a wildfire.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:46.93,0:21:50.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,短短几天内，就在中国社交媒体上疯狂扩散
Dialogue: 3,0:21:52.81,0:21:55.80,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The reaction was explosive.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.81,0:21:55.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,引起舆论哗然
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.80,0:22:01.43,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Suddenly, coworkers, friends, and even family members recognized the men in the videos.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:55.80,0:22:01.43,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这些男人的同事、亲朋好友都认出了他们
Dialogue: 3,0:22:01.43,0:22:03.10,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Husbands were caught cheating.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:01.43,0:22:03.10,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有人是有妇之夫
Dialogue: 3,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.43,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Boyfriends were exposed.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.43,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,或是有女友
Dialogue: 3,0:22:05.43,0:22:08.05,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And one TikToker, with over a million followers, 
Dialogue: 2,0:22:05.43,0:22:08.05,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,甚至有一个抖音百万粉网红
Dialogue: 3,0:22:08.05,0:22:14.06,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,was unmasked when viewers noticed his eyebrows matched perfectly with the man in the footage.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:08.05,0:22:14.06,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,观众通过眉毛认出了他，一毛一样
Dialogue: 3,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.70,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Another was outed to his fiancee.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.70,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还有一个人的未婚妻看到了视频
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.70,0:22:19.05,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Their engagement was instantly called off.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:16.70,0:22:19.05,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这婚是结不成了
Dialogue: 3,0:22:20.60,0:22:23.74,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And the fallout was completely merciless.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:20.60,0:22:23.74,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,这件事造成的结果很残酷
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.74,0:22:25.73,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Lives were ended overnight.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:23.74,0:22:25.73,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,无数人的生活一夜崩塌
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.73,0:22:28.52,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And the internet wasn't forgiving.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:25.73,0:22:28.52,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,而网友们也没说啥好话
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.52,0:22:31.17,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Some viewers mocked the victims.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:28.52,0:22:31.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有人嘲笑受害者
Dialogue: 3,0:22:31.17,0:22:33.85,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Others turned them into memes.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.17,0:22:33.85,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,也有人把他们p成梗图
Dialogue: 3,0:22:33.85,0:22:39.18,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And as their humiliation spread, so too did the legend of Sister Hong.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.85,0:22:39.18,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,随着这些丑事在网上传播，红姐也就成了SSR人物
Dialogue: 3,0:22:39.18,0:22:42.94,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,By July 2025, the scandal wasn't just trending.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.18,0:22:42.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,到7月，红姐不只是“热搜”这么简单
Dialogue: 3,0:22:42.94,0:22:44.76,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,It was everywhere.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.94,0:22:44.76,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,已经无孔不入
Dialogue: 3,0:22:44.76,0:22:47.57,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The hashtag, TopChinesePlatforms.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.76,0:22:47.57,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,#TopChinesePlatforms
Dialogue: 3,0:22:47.57,0:22:49.36,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Teemed spread internationally.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:47.57,0:22:49.36,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,传到了国外
Dialogue: 3,0:22:49.36,0:22:52.50,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,People dressed up as Sister Hong, wearing wigs and masks.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:49.36,0:22:52.50,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,人们开始模仿红姐的妆造
Dialogue: 3,0:22:52.50,0:22:55.45,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Dancing in TikTok parodies.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:52.50,0:22:55.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在抖音模仿、恶搞她
Dialogue: 3,0:22:55.45,0:22:58.19,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And even brands tried to cash in.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:55.45,0:22:58.19,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,甚至有品牌蹭红姐热度
Dialogue: 3,0:22:58.19,0:23:01.80,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And for many, it became a bizarre, collective joke.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:58.19,0:23:01.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,很多人把它当成了一场荒诞的玩笑取乐
Dialogue: 3,0:23:02.38,0:23:06.64,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But for the men exposed, hundreds of them, it was no joke at all.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.38,0:23:06.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,那些男的可笑不出来
Dialogue: 3,0:23:06.64,0:23:08.45,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Their privacy was completely gone.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.64,0:23:08.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,自己的隐私全没了
Dialogue: 3,0:23:08.45,0:23:10.67,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Their reputations were ruined.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:08.45,0:23:10.67,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,身败名裂
Dialogue: 3,0:23:10.67,0:23:16.04,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And what made it worse was the revelation of who Sister Hong really was.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.67,0:23:16.04,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,当红姐的真实身份曝光，这件事更显难蚌本色
Dialogue: 3,0:23:16.04,0:23:19.08,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Because Sister Hong was no woman.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.04,0:23:19.08,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,因为红姐压根就不是女的
Dialogue: 3,0:23:19.08,0:23:25.15,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Beneath the wig and makeup was Jiao, a 38-year-old man from another province.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:19.08,0:23:25.15,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,真实身份为一名38岁的非江苏籍焦姓男子
Dialogue: 3,0:23:25.15,0:23:28.71,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And for years, he kept his disguise intact.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:25.15,0:23:28.71,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,多年来，他的伪装天衣无缝
Dialogue: 3,0:23:28.71,0:23:30.74,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But the videos revealed subtle hints.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.71,0:23:30.74,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但从录像还是能看出来几分端倪
Dialogue: 3,0:23:30.74,0:23:32.21,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Stiff body language.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:30.74,0:23:32.21,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他的动作十分僵硬
Dialogue: 3,0:23:32.21,0:23:33.74,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Strange movements.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:32.21,0:23:33.74,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,举止怪诞
Dialogue: 3,0:23:33.74,0:23:35.61,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,A voice that sometimes slipped.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:33.74,0:23:35.61,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有的时候会夹不住嗓子
Dialogue: 3,0:23:36.96,0:23:38.24,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And the illusion...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:36.96,0:23:38.24,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,最终，他的伪装
Dialogue: 3,0:23:38.24,0:23:39.32,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Cracked.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:38.24,0:23:39.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}崩塌了
Dialogue: 3,0:23:41.68,0:23:43.63,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Speculation ran wild.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:41.68,0:23:43.63,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,甚至有谣言说
Dialogue: 3,0:23:43.63,0:23:45.40,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Was he actually this old?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.63,0:23:45.40,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他其实比38岁大
Dialogue: 3,0:23:45.40,0:23:47.30,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Was he hiding a disguise?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:45.40,0:23:47.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,还有别的马甲
Dialogue: 3,0:23:47.30,0:23:51.31,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Or was the disguise just a cover for something more sinister?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:47.30,0:23:51.31,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,或者说，红姐这个马甲就是用来掩盖那一层身份的？
Dialogue: 3,0:23:52.46,0:23:55.92,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And by now, rumors overshadowed reality.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:52.46,0:23:55.92,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,此时，传言早已淹没了事实
Dialogue: 3,0:23:55.92,0:23:58.90,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But police were about to settle the question.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:55.92,0:23:58.90,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,真相要交给警方揭露
Dialogue: 3,0:23:59.85,0:24:02.59,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,On July 6th, 2025.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:59.85,0:24:02.59,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,2025年7月6日
Dialogue: 3,0:24:02.59,0:24:06.54,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Nanjing Nianjing police announced the arrest.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:02.59,0:24:06.54,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,南京警方宣布逮捕嫌疑人
Dialogue: 3,0:24:06.54,0:24:08.60,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,The suspect was confirmed.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:06.54,0:24:08.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,正式确认了红姐的身份
Dialogue: 3,0:24:08.60,0:24:11.84,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,A 38-year-old man named Jiao.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:08.60,0:24:11.84,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,38岁焦性男子
Dialogue: 3,0:24:12.44,0:24:17.39,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,He was charged with secretly filming and distributing obscene content.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:12.44,0:24:17.39,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,罪名是偷拍「传播淫秽物品」
Dialogue: 3,0:24:18.34,0:24:22.26,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But by then, the internet had already mythologized him as...
Dialogue: 2,0:24:18.34,0:24:22.26,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但在那之前，网络上早已把他神化成另一个人物
Dialogue: 3,0:24:22.26,0:24:24.63,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Red Uncle.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:22.26,0:24:24.63,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,红大爷
Dialogue: 3,0:24:24.63,0:24:27.27,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Some swore he infected men with HIV.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:24.63,0:24:27.27,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有人说他把HIV传给了那些男的
Dialogue: 3,0:24:27.27,0:24:31.10,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Although police stressed the claims were exaggerated.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:27.27,0:24:31.10,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但是警方说，该说法与事实严重不符
Dialogue: 3,0:24:31.12,0:24:33.28,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And others clung to the viral number.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:31.12,0:24:33.28,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有人传的数字很夸张
Dialogue: 3,0:24:33.28,0:24:35.72,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,1,691 men.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:33.28,0:24:35.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,共有1691名男子
Dialogue: 3,0:24:36.96,0:24:39.81,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Officials suggested the rail count was far lower.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:36.96,0:24:39.81,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,警方表示实际数字远低于此
Dialogue: 3,0:24:39.81,0:24:42.08,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But the damage was already done.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:39.81,0:24:42.08,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,再解释也没用了
Dialogue: 3,0:24:42.93,0:24:47.75,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,In the public image, Sister Hong had already become a monster of legend.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:42.93,0:24:47.75,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,在公众眼中，红姐早已变成了一个传说中的怪物
Dialogue: 3,0:24:49.71,0:24:54.62,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But after the arrest, police actually revealed another disturbing possibility.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:49.71,0:24:54.62,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但在他被捕后，警方披露了另一种令人不安的可能
Dialogue: 3,0:24:54.62,0:25:01.89,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,After the rumors spread, it came out that Sister Hong might have actually been HIV positive.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:54.62,0:25:01.89,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,有小道消息称，红姐可能感染了HIV病毒
Dialogue: 3,0:25:01.89,0:25:06.23,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And if true, the consequences would be catastrophic.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:01.89,0:25:06.23,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,如果这是真的，后果将不堪设想
Dialogue: 3,0:25:07.12,0:25:10.88,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And for many, most people's life were completely ruined.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:07.12,0:25:10.88,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,红姐视频里很多男的，其实已经社死了
Dialogue: 3,0:25:11.52,0:25:15.38,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And the tragedy was that many of these men never knew they were being recorded.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:11.52,0:25:15.38,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,最悲哀的是，许多男的从头到尾都被蒙在鼓里
Dialogue: 3,0:25:16.01,0:25:17.97,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,That they had been lured in by deception.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:16.01,0:25:17.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他们也是上了红姐的当
Dialogue: 3,0:25:18.82,0:25:22.29,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Only to have their faces plastered across the internet for millions to gawk at.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:18.82,0:25:22.29,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}却被无数网民拿来做表情包
Dialogue: 3,0:25:24.38,0:25:27.32,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But as we all know, the internet moves fast.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:24.38,0:25:27.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但众所周知，网络梗的寿命很短
Dialogue: 3,0:25:27.32,0:25:29.80,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And within weeks, the memes slowed down.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:27.32,0:25:29.80,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,几周后，红姐相关梗的热度就下去了
Dialogue: 3,0:25:29.80,0:25:32.10,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,New scandals replaced Sister Hong in the trending feed.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:29.80,0:25:32.10,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,新的丑闻接连出现，把红姐挤出热搜
Dialogue: 3,0:25:33.18,0:25:37.30,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,But for the victims, the consequences remained permanent.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:33.18,0:25:37.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,然而对受害者来说，他们遭受的伤害永远无法治愈
Dialogue: 3,0:25:37.30,0:25:40.54,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Their faces, once anonymous, are still floating online.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:37.30,0:25:40.54,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,原本匿名的面孔，如今依然在网上传播
Dialogue: 3,0:25:41.92,0:25:46.98,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And for some, the looming possibility of infection is a shadow they can't escape.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:41.92,0:25:46.98,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,甚至是部分人一辈子都摆脱不了的噩梦
Dialogue: 3,0:25:48.44,0:25:52.37,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And as for Jiao, the man who was behind the makeup, wigs and mask.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:48.44,0:25:52.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,但是隐藏在浓妆、假发、口罩背后的焦某
Dialogue: 3,0:25:52.37,0:25:55.05,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,His story is still unfinished.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:52.37,0:25:55.05,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他的故事仍未结束
Dialogue: 3,0:25:55.05,0:25:57.45,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,He could spend the rest of his life behind bars.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:55.05,0:25:57.45,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,他可能将在牢狱中度过余生
Dialogue: 3,0:25:57.45,0:25:58.60,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,Or even worse.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:57.45,0:25:58.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,甚至更糟
Dialogue: 3,0:26:00.17,0:26:05.62,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,And in the end, the Sister Hong saga isn't just about deception or scandal.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:00.17,0:26:05.62,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,归根结底，红姐事件不仅仅是一个关于欺骗或丑闻的故事
Dialogue: 3,0:26:05.62,0:26:09.64,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,A reminder of how quickly the internet can transform tragedy into entertainment.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:05.62,0:26:09.64,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,它提醒我们，互联网拿悲剧当乐子的速度有多快
Dialogue: 3,0:26:10.31,0:26:13.82,Default-L2,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And how, once it does, there's no way back.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:10.31,0:26:13.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦娱乐化，就再也回不去了
Dialogue: 3,0:26:43.17,0:26:44.07,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,直播
Dialogue: 2,0:26:43.17,0:26:44.07,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Livestreams.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:44.07,0:26:48.70,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,它本应是被用来连接起我们的 窥探他人生活的窗口
Dialogue: 2,0:26:44.07,0:26:48.70,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Are supposed to connect us. They're windows into someone's life.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:49.12,0:26:51.87,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,被用于带来欢笑 集思广益和寻欢作乐
Dialogue: 2,0:26:49.12,0:26:51.87,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Meant for laughter. Advice. And entertainment.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:55.42,0:26:58.05,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,但就在2021年秋的中国
Dialogue: 2,0:26:55.42,0:26:58.05,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,But in China. In the fall of 2021.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:58.55,0:27:02.05,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,有一场直播并没有将人们连接起来 而是将其困住
Dialogue: 2,0:26:58.55,0:27:02.05,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,One broadcast. Didn't connect. It trapped.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:03.15,0:27:05.70,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,那是一场观众成为了参与者的直播
Dialogue: 2,0:27:03.15,0:27:05.70,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,A livestream. Where viewers became participants.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:06.07,0:27:08.85,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,悲剧便在其中实时上演
Dialogue: 2,0:27:06.07,0:27:08.85,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And tragedy unfolded. In real time.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:12.47,0:27:17.72,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,罗小猫猫子 一位23岁的时尚网红
Dialogue: 2,0:27:12.47,0:27:17.72,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Lu Xiaomiao Miaozhi. A 23-year-old fashion influencer.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:17.80,0:27:22.70,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,在抖音（中国版TikTok）上拥有超过60万粉丝
Dialogue: 2,0:27:17.80,0:27:22.70,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,With over 600,000 followers. On Douyin. China's version of TikTok.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:25.15,0:27:28.72,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,她在观众面前活泼爱笑且十分俏皮
Dialogue: 2,0:27:25.15,0:27:28.72,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And to her audience. She was upbeat, smiling, playful people.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:29.70,0:27:33.22,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,但在镜头之外 她正与严重的抑郁症作斗争
Dialogue: 2,0:27:29.70,0:27:33.22,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,But off screen. She was fighting severe depression.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:35.07,0:27:38.52,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,那年早些时候 她曾住院两个多月
Dialogue: 2,0:27:35.07,0:27:38.52,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,She had been hospitalized for more than two months earlier that year.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:41.40,0:27:42.89,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,用她自己的话说 就是
Dialogue: 2,0:27:41.40,0:27:42.89,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And in her own words:
Dialogue: 3,0:27:43.53,0:27:46.30,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,"那你们看到我开心的样子 其实都是为了给你们看到啊"
Dialogue: 2,0:27:43.53,0:27:46.30,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,I appear to be happy. But this is all for show.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:47.05,0:27:50.65,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,"我希望大家看到我的视频是开心的 是快乐的"
Dialogue: 2,0:27:47.05,0:27:50.65,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,I hope everyone. Will be happy. When they see my videos.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:51.40,0:27:53.70,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,"是知道我也是快乐的"
Dialogue: 2,0:27:51.40,0:27:53.70,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And will see that I am happy too.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:54.10,0:27:56.62,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,"可是最近我真的绷不住了"
Dialogue: 2,0:27:54.10,0:27:56.62,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,But, I cannot hold on anymore.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:58.22,0:28:00.00,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,在她最后一次直播前几小时
Dialogue: 2,0:27:58.22,0:28:00.00,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Hours before her final stream.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:00.80,0:28:03.77,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,她发布了一条名为"大概是最后一条了吧"的视频
Dialogue: 2,0:28:00.80,0:28:03.77,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,She posted a video calling it: Probably my last.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:04.57,0:28:06.70,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,并感谢了粉丝们的陪伴
Dialogue: 2,0:28:04.57,0:28:06.70,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And thanked her fans for their company.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:09.85,0:28:12.37,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,2021年10月14日
Dialogue: 2,0:28:09.85,0:28:12.37,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,On October 14th, 2021.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:13.27,0:28:15.90,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,罗小猫猫子开播了 她拿着一个瓶子
Dialogue: 2,0:28:13.27,0:28:15.90,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Lu went live. She held a bottle.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:16.20,0:28:18.10,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,里面混着农药和饮料
Dialogue: 2,0:28:16.20,0:28:18.10,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Mixed with pesticide and a drink.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:19.77,0:28:23.60,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,一些观众劝她停下来 但另一些人却恰恰相反
Dialogue: 2,0:28:19.77,0:28:23.60,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Some viewers urged her to stop. But others did the exact opposite.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:24.02,0:28:31.72,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,用诸如"搞快点" "瓶子里不会是尿吧" "要喝快喝"之类的弹幕怂恿她
Dialogue: 2,0:28:24.02,0:28:31.72,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Egging her on with comments like. Drink it quickly. There is no urine in the bottle. Do it if you are going to do it.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:33.12,0:28:35.80,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,然后她就在直播中喝了下去
Dialogue: 2,0:28:33.12,0:28:35.80,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And, she swallowed it, on stream.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:36.87,0:28:38.30,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,即使有弹幕刷屏
Dialogue: 2,0:28:36.87,0:28:38.30,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And even as the chat scrolled.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:39.07,0:28:42.17,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,她自己也在下播后叫了救护车
Dialogue: 2,0:28:39.07,0:28:42.17,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,She herself, called the ambulance after ending the broadcast.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:44.12,0:28:47.95,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,医生试图抢救她 但为时已晚
Dialogue: 2,0:28:44.12,0:28:47.95,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Doctors tried to save her. But it was already too late.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:48.67,0:28:51.75,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,她的家人表示是直播间里的喷子将她逼到了绝境
Dialogue: 2,0:28:48.67,0:28:51.75,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Her family said the trolls in the chat. Pushed her over the edge.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:52.55,0:28:55.50,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,其他人则猜测这与她同前任分手有关
Dialogue: 2,0:28:52.55,0:28:55.50,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Others speculated it was connected to her breakup with an ex.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:56.62,0:28:59.45,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,但她家人坚称这不是原因所在
Dialogue: 2,0:28:56.62,0:28:59.45,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,But her relatives insisted that this wasn't the reason.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:01.40,0:29:04.00,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,她的一位朋友说 罗小猫猫子本不打算结束自己的生命
Dialogue: 2,0:29:01.40,0:29:04.00,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,One friend claimed that Lu did not intend to end her life.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:04.47,0:29:05.57,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,那是一场作秀
Dialogue: 2,0:29:04.47,0:29:05.57,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,That it was an act.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:06.25,0:29:08.60,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,是为了引起她前男友注意而上演的
Dialogue: 2,0:29:06.25,0:29:08.60,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,That was staged to get her ex-boyfriend's attention.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:10.02,0:29:13.65,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,但一旦有评论开始鼓励她 她就真的照做了
Dialogue: 2,0:29:10.02,0:29:13.65,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,But once the comments encouraged her. She went through with it.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:16.67,0:29:18.15,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,截图在网上疯传
Dialogue: 2,0:29:16.67,0:29:18.15,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,The screenshots went viral.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:18.65,0:29:20.67,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,有一个手握毒药的年轻女子
Dialogue: 2,0:29:18.65,0:29:20.67,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,A young woman, holding poison.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:21.35,0:29:23.85,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,而陌生人们却打出侮辱和挑衅的文字
Dialogue: 2,0:29:21.35,0:29:23.85,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,While strangers, type insults and dares.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:26.22,0:29:29.67,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,这场风波堪称完美 它是脆弱与残忍的交汇
Dialogue: 2,0:29:26.22,0:29:29.67,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,It's a perfect storm. For vulnerability and cruelty.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:31.05,0:29:34.67,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,观众的嘲弄将她的痛苦化为笑料
Dialogue: 2,0:29:31.05,0:29:34.67,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,The audience's jeering. Turned her pain into entertainment.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:36.55,0:29:39.20,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,而就在在罗小猫猫子的遗体在山东火化后
Dialogue: 2,0:29:36.55,0:29:39.20,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And, after Lu's cremation at Shandong.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:39.37,0:29:44.20,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,这场悲剧出现了更黑暗的转折——她的骨灰被盗了
Dialogue: 2,0:29:39.37,0:29:44.20,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Her tragedy took an even darker turn. Her ashes were stolen.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:46.05,0:29:50.17,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,一名殡仪馆工作人员 一名灵车司机 和一名当地的殡葬师
Dialogue: 2,0:29:46.05,0:29:50.17,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,A funeral home worker. A heurist driver. And a local undertaker.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:50.25,0:29:53.25,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,共同组成了警方后来所称为的"骨灰供应链"
Dialogue: 2,0:29:50.25,0:29:53.25,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Formed what police later called. A bone ash supply chain.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:54.40,0:29:55.60,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,他们调换了她的骨灰
Dialogue: 2,0:29:54.40,0:29:55.60,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,They swapped her remains.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:55.60,0:29:57.92,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,并试图将其出售供一种民俗所用
Dialogue: 2,0:29:55.60,0:29:57.92,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And tried to sell them. into an underground practice.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:57.92,0:30:02.25,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,这种习俗仍然盛行于中国的部分地区 即"冥婚"
Dialogue: 2,0:29:57.92,0:30:02.25,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Still thriving in parts of China. Which is called a ghost marriage.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:04.22,0:30:06.67,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,冥婚可以追溯到商代
Dialogue: 2,0:30:04.22,0:30:06.67,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Ghost marriages date back to the Shang dynasty.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:07.07,0:30:10.32,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,其所寄托的东西很朴素 却非常令人不安
Dialogue: 2,0:30:07.07,0:30:10.32,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And the belief is pretty simple. But very disturbing.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:10.92,0:30:12.80,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,那就是"一个未婚的灵魂是不得安宁的"
Dialogue: 2,0:30:10.92,0:30:12.80,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,An unmarried soul is restless.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:13.50,0:30:15.45,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,一个年轻男子独自下葬
Dialogue: 2,0:30:13.50,0:30:15.45,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,A young man. Buried alone.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:15.97,0:30:17.85,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,则可能会给他的家庭带来不幸
Dialogue: 2,0:30:15.97,0:30:17.85,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,Could bring misfortune to his family.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:18.87,0:30:19.96,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,而为了解决这个问题
Dialogue: 2,0:30:18.87,0:30:19.96,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And to fix this, 
Dialogue: 3,0:30:20.40,0:30:25.65,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,亲属会安排一场与年轻女子的遗体甚至只是骨灰的婚事
Dialogue: 2,0:30:20.40,0:30:25.65,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,relatives arrange a marriage with the body. Or even just the ashes of a young woman.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:29.92,0:30:32.92,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,一场有陌生人在其中怂恿的直播
Dialogue: 2,0:30:29.92,0:30:32.92,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,A livestream. Where strangers urged her on.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:34.37,0:30:37.20,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,和一场骨灰被为了牟利而盗走的丧事
Dialogue: 2,0:30:34.37,0:30:37.20,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,A cremation. Where her ashes were stolen for profit.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:37.87,0:30:40.90,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,无论是生是死 罗小猫猫子都被消费了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:37.87,0:30:40.90,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,In life.And in death.Lu was consumed.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:41.57,0:30:46.95,Default-Import1,atg1,0,0,0,,这就是为什么她的故事成了中国互联网上最黑暗的悲剧之一
Dialogue: 2,0:30:41.57,0:30:46.95,Default-L2-Import1,atg2,0,0,0,,And that's what makes her story. One of the most darkest tragedies.On the Chinese internet.